{"tid":2334642,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[禁蒙面法] 政府歡迎終院裁決　確立《緊急法》合憲性","createTime":"2020-12-21T09:49:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T10:04:24.000Z","uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"07bb293a86f04d380a1f5e5e7dc5f299fc20ecc6","tid":2334642,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T09:49:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201221/417710539699916800769185.jpeg/8hKtjdQjkHE6l58mkDOTJz7zCX1L-hccZ8MnimfDJ4o?v=w1440r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201221%2F417710539699916800769185.jpeg%2F8hKtjdQjkHE6l58mkDOTJz7zCX1L-hccZ8MnimfDJ4o%3Fv%3Dw1440r16_9&h=ac47fae9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去年反修例運動期間，政府引用《緊急情況規例條例》（緊急法）訂立《禁止蒙面規例》（禁蒙面法），禁止市民在遊行時蒙面。終審法院今日（21日）就相關司法覆核案頒下判辭，裁定《緊急法》不違憲，無論在和平合法或非法集會，皆不能蒙面。<br />\n<br />\n保安局回應指，歡迎終審法院的判決，指裁決確立《緊急情況規例條例》，以及禁止在公眾集會中蒙面的合憲性。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WPMWNLY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWPMWNLY.gif&h=7ad532e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n保安局表示：「政府歡迎終審法院的判決。法院確立《緊急情況規例條例》的合憲性，並確認《禁止蒙面規例》禁止在非法集結、未經批准集結、多於50 人的公眾集會及多於30人的公眾遊行中使用蒙面物品的合憲性和相稱性。」"},{"pid":"4f39c5219b8ed3b404a5ae6211c13a22444ab9b1","tid":2334642,"uid":127333,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T10:04:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AOQ4WKq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAOQ4WKq.jpg&h=4b6d59d9&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}